解散了
Broke up?

16:12.030 --> 16:14.080
像乐队那样吗  像披头士那样吗
Like a band? Like... Like the Beatles?

16:14.080 --> 16:15.810
队长和我闹得很僵
Cap and I fell out hard.

16:17.120 --> 16:18.610
我们现在不说话了
We're not on speaking terms.

16:19.580 --> 16:21.860
托尼  听我说
Tony, listen to me.

16:23.210 --> 16:24.360
托尔死了
Thor's gone.

16:26.340 --> 16:27.170
灭霸要来了
Thanos is coming.

16:27.170 --> 16:29.490
你跟不跟谁说话都无所谓了
It doesn't matter who you're talking to or not.

16:46.440 --> 16:47.590
翻盖手机
Flip phone.

16:51.350 --> 16:53.270
<b>史蒂夫·罗杰斯</b>

17:08.420 --> 17:10.830
博士  你是在自己动头发吗
Say, Doc, you wouldn't happen to be moving your hair, would ya?

17:11.840 --> 17:14.160
现在没有
Not at the moment, no.

17:47.000 --> 17:47.820
你没事吧
You okay?

17:49.710 --> 17:50.570
-帮帮他  -班纳
- Help him! - Banner!

17:50.590 --> 17:52.330
-王  精神点  -去吧  我们能行
- Wong! Look alive! - Go, go! We got it!

17:52.550 --> 17:53.550
星期五  什么情况
Friday, what am I looking at?

17:53.550 --> 17:55.330
不确定  我还在查看
Not sure. I'm working on it.

17:55.930 --> 17:57.140
你最好把时间宝石
You might wanna put that Time Stone

17:57.140 --> 17:58.670
塞后兜里  博士
in your back pocket, Doc!

17:58.810 --> 18:00.080
还是用它更好
Might wanna use it.

18:27.500 --> 18:30.050
内德  我需要你分散大家的注意
Ned, hey. I need you to cause a distraction.

18:30.050 --> 18:31.410
我去
Holy shit.

18:31.630 --> 18:33.070
我们都要死了
We're all gonna die!

18:33.340 --> 18:34.550
那里有架飞船
There's a spaceship!

18:34.550 --> 18:36.240
-怎么回事啊  -天呐
- What's going on? - Oh, my God!

18:44.520 --> 18:45.730
你们这些孩子怎么回事
What's the matter with you kids?

18:45.730 --> 18:48.010
没见过宇宙飞船啊
You never seen a spaceship before?

18:59.990 --> 19:02.620
星期五  疏散43街以南的群众
Friday, evac anyone south of 43rd Street.

19:02.620 --> 19:03.700
通知应急人员
Notify first responders.

19:03.710 --> 19:04.560
好
Will do.

19:33.240 --> 19:35.970
听我说  你们应当开心
Hear me and rejoice.

19:37.530 --> 19:39.110
你们即将死在
You are about to die

19:39.120 --> 19:41.560
灭霸的孩子手下
at the hands of the Children of Thanos.

19:42.160 --> 19:43.350
心怀感激吧
Be thankful...

19:43.870 --> 19:46.870
你们毫无意义的人生将贡献...
that your meaningless lives are now contributing...

19:46.870 --> 19:49.650
抱歉  地球今天歇业
I'm sorry, Earth is closed today.

19:49.710 --> 19:52.590
你们最好收拾东西滚蛋
You better pack it up and get outta here.

19:52.590 --> 19:53.780
宝石守护者
Stonekeeper.

19:54.550 --> 19:57.010
这喋喋不休的动物能替你说话吗
Does this chattering animal speak for you?

19:57.010 --> 19:58.830
当然不  我想说什么自己说
Certainly not. I speak for myself.

19:59.550 --> 20:01.960
你们在这座城市和这颗星球都不受欢迎
You're trespassing in this city and on this planet.

20:02.810 --> 20:04.390
就是滚蛋的意思  章鱼哥
He means get lost, Squidward.

20:04.390 --> 20:05.710
他让我厌烦
He exhausts me.

20:06.430 --> 20:07.630
把宝石拿来给我
Bring me the stone.

20:09.400 --> 20:10.420
班纳  你想出手吗
Banner, you want a piece?

20:12.110 --> 20:12.980
并不想
No, not really.

20:12.980 --> 20:14.610
但我什么时候如愿过了
But when do I ever get what I want?

20:14.610 --> 20:15.430
这就对了
That's right.

20:16.320 --> 20:17.780
好  加把劲
Okay. Push!

20:17.780 --> 20:18.640
好久没见了
It's been a while.

20:19.490 --> 20:20.850
能再见到你会很高兴的  哥们
It's gonna be good to have you, buddy.

20:20.990 --> 20:21.680
好吧
Okay.

20:22.280 --> 20:24.980
容我...我得集中精神
Let me just... I need to concentrate here for a second.

20:25.080 --> 20:26.600
来啊  拜托
Come on, come on, man.

20:28.210 --> 20:29.150
天呐
God!

20:29.830 --> 20:30.610
那家伙呢
Where's your guy?

20:32.460 --> 20:34.040
我不知道  我们最近有点问题
I don't know. We've sorta been having a thing.

20:34.050 --> 20:35.170
-现在不是有问题的时候  -我知道
- It's no time for a thing. - I know.

20:35.170 --> 20:36.530
那才是问题  来吧
That's the thing right there. Let's go.

20:44.060 --> 20:45.180
哥们  你让我巫师面前下不来台了
Dude, you're embarrassing me in front of the wizards.

20:45.180 --> 20:47.430
托尼  抱歉  不是我不能  就是他不想
Tony, I'm sorry. Either I can't or he won't.

20:47.430 --> 20:48.170
没事的
It's okay.

20:48.270 --> 20:50.850
退后吧  替我看着点他  谢谢
Hey, stand down. Keep an eye on him. Thank you.

20:50.850 --> 20:52.510
-交给我吧  -该死
- I have him. - Damn it.

21:20.010 --> 21:21.370
那是哪来的
Where'd that come from?

21:21.430 --> 21:22.220
是纳米科技
It's nanotech.

21:22.220 --> 21:24.160
喜欢吗  是我...
You like it? A little something I...

21:27.270 --> 21:30.590
班纳博士  如果你的绿朋友不打算来了
Doctor Banner, if the rest of your green friend won't be joining us...

21:40.400 --> 21:41.780
快把宝石送走
Gotta get that stone outta here, now.

21:41.780 --> 21:43.160
我人在宝石在
It stays with me.

21:43.160 --> 21:44.390
没错  再见
Exactly. Bye.

21:53.920 --> 21:55.150
托尼  你没事吧
Tony, you okay?

21:55.420 --> 21:57.380
-情况怎么样  是好是坏  -可好了
- How we doing? Good? Bad? - Really, really good.

21:57.380 --> 21:58.800
可好了  你想不想帮忙啊
Really good. Do you plan on helping out?

21:58.800 --> 22:00.110
我也想  他不肯出来
I'm trying. He won't come out.

22:01.720 --> 22:02.410
锤子
Hammer.

22:10.730 --> 22:13.690
拜托  绿巨人  你这是干什么啊
Come on, Hulk! What are you doing to me?

22:13.690 --> 22:16.190
出来啊  出来啊
Come out! Come out! Come out!

22:16.190 --> 22:18.090
不要
No!

22:22.070 --> 22:23.890
什么叫"不要"
What do you mean, "No"?

22:29.790 --> 22:31.540
好啊  斯塔克先生  你好吗
Hey, man. What's up, Mr. Stark?

22:31.540 --> 22:32.660
孩子  你哪冒出来的
Kid, where'd you come from?

22:32.660 --> 22:34.400
我们当时正要去现代艺术博物馆
A field trip to MoMA.

22:36.250 --> 22:38.500
这家伙什么毛病  斯塔克先生
What is this guy's problem, Mr. Stark?

22:38.500 --> 22:39.710
他是外太空来的
Uh, he's from space.

22:39.710 --> 22:42.070
他是来偷一个巫师的项链的
He came here to steal a necklace from a wizard.

23:08.660 --> 23:10.490
你的能力很有意思
Your powers are quaint.

23:10.490 --> 23:12.520
你一定很受孩子的喜欢吧
You must be popular with children.

23:15.250 --> 23:17.120
虽然是简单的咒语  但不可攻破
It's a simple spell but quite unbreakable.

23:17.130 --> 23:19.400
那我就先杀了你再拿
Then I'll take it off your corpse.

23:32.140 --> 23:33.200
你会发现
You'll find

23:33.200 --> 23:34.150
想解除
removing

23:34.420 --> 23:35.980
一个死人的咒语
a dead man's spell

23:36.620 --> 23:37.690
会很困难
troublesome.

23:37.690 --> 23:39.670
你会生不如死
You'll only wish you were dead.

23:49.950 --> 23:50.850
不
No!

23:54.750 --> 23:55.950
孩子  就是那个巫师  快去
Kid, that's the wizard. Get on it.

23:55.960 --> 23:56.650
去了
On it!

24:05.300 --> 24:06.240
好过分
Not cool.

24:11.220 --> 24:11.950
抓到你了
Gotcha!

24:13.310 --> 24:14.080
等等
Wait!

24:21.860 --> 24:24.630
斯塔克先生  我被光吸上去了
Uh, Mr. Stark, I'm being beamed up.

24:24.900 --> 24:25.930
撑着  孩子
Hang on, kid.

24:46.010 --> 24:47.570
王  我婚礼你一定要来
Wong, you're invited to my wedding.

24:55.560 --> 24:56.870
给我点动力  星期五
Give me a little juice, Friday.

25:05.480 --> 25:07.260
启动17A
Unlock 17:A.

25:19.910 --> 25:21.580
彼得  放手吧  我来接住你
Pete, you gotta let go. I'm gonna catch you.

25:21.580 --> 25:23.280
但你叫我救巫师的
But you said save the wizard!

25:24.500 --> 25:25.490
我不能呼吸了
I can't breathe.

25:26.300 --> 25:28.240
我们太高了  你要没空气了
We're too high up. You're running out of air.

25:29.260 --> 25:31.370
是啊  这讲得通
Yeah. That makes sense.

25:48.530 --> 25:50.590
斯塔克先生  这里面闻起来像新车
Mr. Stark, it smells like a new car in here!

25:50.820 --> 25:51.820
一路顺风  孩子
Happy trails, kid.

25:51.820 --> 25:53.350
-星期五  送他回家  -好
- Friday, send him home. - Yep.

25:54.240 --> 25:55.270
拜托
Oh, come on!

26:03.710 --> 26:05.790
老板  波茨小姐来电
Boss, incoming call from Miss Potts.

26:05.790 --> 26:07.000
托尼  天呐
Tony? Oh, my God.

26:07.000 --> 26:08.420
你没事吧  怎么回事啊
Are you all right? What's going on?

26:08.420 --> 26:09.000
我没事
Yeah, I'm fine.

26:09.010 --> 26:11.470
但我们8:30的预约可能得延期了
I just think we might have to push our 8:30 res.

26:11.470 --> 26:12.200
为什么
Why?

26:12.380 --> 26:15.540
就是我可能一时半会儿回不去
Just 'cause I'll probably not make it back for a while.

26:16.510 --> 26:17.870
告诉我你没在那艘飞船上
Tell me you're not on that ship.

26:18.180 --> 26:18.720
嗯
Yeah.

26:18.720 --> 26:20.210
天呐  不  告诉我你没在那艘飞船上
God, no, please tell me you're not on the ship.

26:20.220 --> 26:21.750
亲爱的  对不起
Honey, I'm sorry.

26:22.020 --> 26:22.850
对不起  我不知道该怎么说
I'm sorry, I don't know what to say.

26:22.850 --> 26:24.690
给我回来  托尼  我发誓
Come back here, Tony. I swear to God.

26:24.690 --> 26:26.710
-派珀  -赶紧给我回来
- Pep. - Come back here right now.

26:27.070 --> 26:28.230
回来
Come back.

26:28.230 --> 26:29.840
老板  信号要断了
Boss, we're losing her.

26:30.990 --> 26:32.010
我也去
I'm going too.

26:41.500 --> 26:42.310
天呐
Oh, my God!

26:47.090 --> 26:48.860
我就该待在校车上
I shoulda stayed on the bus.

27:03.390 --> 27:04.210
你去哪
Where you going?

27:05.100 --> 27:06.460
时间宝石被夺走了
The Time Stone's been taken.

27:06.810 --> 27:08.420
圣殿无人守护
The Sanctum remains unguarded.

27:09.110 --> 27:10.090
你要怎么办
What will you do?

27:11.360 --> 27:12.800
我要打个电话
I'm gonna make a call.

27:17.100 --> 27:19.940
<b>史蒂夫·罗杰斯</b>

27:25.990 --> 27:28.860
外  太  空

27:53.400 --> 27:54.340
唱吧  德拉克斯
Sing it, Drax!

28:07.210 --> 28:08.620
我们为什么要这么做来着
Why are we doing this again?

28:08.620 --> 28:10.330
有人发了求救信号  火箭
It's a distress signal, Rocket.

28:10.330 --> 28:11.420
可能有人有危险
Someone could be dying.

28:11.420 --> 28:13.920
这我懂  但我们为什么要来
I get that, but why are we doing it?

28:13.920 --> 28:14.990
因为我们是好人
'Cause we're nice.

28:15.840 --> 28:16.720
或许求救的人
And maybe whoever it is

28:16.720 --> 28:18.510
会给我们点切达奶酪作为感谢
will give us a little cheddar cheese for our effort.

28:18.510 --> 28:21.000
-这不是重点  -这不是重点
- Which isn't the point. - Which isn't the point.

28:21.300 --> 28:23.220
如果他不给谢礼
I mean, if he doesn't pony up...

28:23.220 --> 28:24.140
我们就夺他的船
We take his ship.

28:24.140 --> 28:26.270
-没错  -正确
- Exactly! - Bingo!

28:26.270 --> 28:27.130
好嘞
All right!

28:30.310 --> 28:31.760
我们要到了
We are arriving.

28:32.320 --> 28:33.020
好了  护卫队
All right, Guardians,

28:33.020 --> 28:34.690
别忘了  情况可能很危险
don't forget this might be dangerous...

28:34.690 --> 28:36.840
大家都凶起来
so let's put on our mean faces.

28:39.350 --> 28:41.100
<b>防卫者</b>

28:42.200 --> 28:43.660
格鲁特  马上把那玩意放起来
Groot, put that thing away, now.

28:43.660 --> 28:44.850
别让我再说你
I don't wanna tell you again.

28:45.290 --> 28:46.020
格鲁特
Groot.

28:46.080 --> 28:47.690
我是格鲁特
I am Groot!

28:47.870 --> 28:48.860
怎么说话呢
Language!

28:50.040 --> 28:51.750
你胆子不小  小子
You got some acorns on you, kid.

28:51.750 --> 28:53.250
自从你开始分泌树液
Ever since you got a little sap,

28:53.250 --> 28:54.990
你就变成了个小混蛋
you're a total d-hole.

28:55.460 --> 28:58.740
再这么下去  我把那玩意给你砸了
Now, keep it up, and I'm gonna smash that thing to pieces.

29:05.930 --> 29:06.960
发生了什么
What happened?

29:11.270 --> 29:12.420
天呐
Oh, my God.

29:18.240 --> 29:20.260
看来我们别想拿钱了
Looks like we're not getting paid.

29:22.370 --> 29:24.200
开雨刷  开雨刷
Wipers! Wipers!

29:24.200 --> 29:24.980
把它弄掉
Get it off.

29:32.290 --> 29:34.610
这哥们怎么会还活着
How the hell is this dude still alive?

29:35.210 --> 29:36.610
他不是个"哥们"
He is not a dude.

29:37.170 --> 29:38.280
你是个哥们
You're a dude.

29:38.710 --> 29:41.530
这  是个男人
This... This is a man.

29:42.510 --> 29:45.250
一个帅气的肌肉男
A handsome, muscular man.

29:45.390 --> 29:46.050
我也挺肌肉的
I'm muscular.

29:46.060 --> 29:47.310
你骗谁呢  奎尔
But who are you kidding, Quill?

29:47.310 --> 29:49.100
你再吃一个三明治就是一身肥膘了
You're one sandwich away from fat.

29:49.100 --> 29:49.930
得了吧
Yeah, right.

29:49.930 --> 29:51.770
没错  奎尔  你是胖了点
It's true, Quill. You have put on weight.

29:51.770 --> 29:52.500
什么
What?

29:54.940 --> 29:56.340
卡魔拉  你也觉得我...
Gamora, do you think I'm...

29:59.190 --> 30:02.470
他很焦虑  生气
He is anxious, angry.

30:02.740 --> 30:06.020
他失去了很多  非常愧疚
He feels tremendous loss and guilt.

30:06.700 --> 30:09.560
简直就像一个海盗跟一个天使生了个孩子
It's like a pirate had a baby with an angel.

30:10.710 --> 30:12.540
这对我真是一记警钟啊  好吧
This is a real wake-up call for me. Okay.

30:12.540 --> 30:15.380
我去买个博飞健身器  认真减肥
I'm gonna get a Bowflex. I'm gonna commit.

30:15.380 --> 30:16.670
再去弄个哑铃
I'm gonna get some dumbbells.

30:16.670 --> 30:18.130
你知道哑铃是不能吃的吧
You know you can't eat dumbbells, right?

30:18.130 --> 30:21.550
他的肌肉就像是柯塔蒂金属纤维做的
It's like his muscles are made of Cotati metal fibers.

30:21.550 --> 30:23.530
别给他的肌肉按摩了
Stop massaging his muscles.

30:25.430 --> 30:26.160
弄醒他
Wake him up.

30:29.180 --> 30:30.040
醒来
Wake.

30:47.620 --> 30:49.520
你们是谁
Who the hell are you guys?

30:52.790 --> 30:56.150
自从我认识灭霸  他就只有一个目标
The entire time I knew Thanos, he only ever had one goal.

30:56.540 --> 30:58.040
让宇宙获得平衡
To bring balance to the universe

30:58.040 --> 31:00.150
方法是抹去一半生命
by wiping out half of all life.

31:00.880 --> 31:03.370
他以前会一个个星球地杀人
He used to kill people planet by planet,

31:03.470 --> 31:05.330
一次次地进行屠杀
massacre by massacre.

31:05.380 --> 31:06.580
包括我的星球
Including my own.

31:06.680 --> 31:08.550
如果他拿到全部六颗无限宝石
If he gets all six Infinity Stones...

31:08.550 --> 31:11.210
那他打一个响指就能实现愿望
he can do it with the snap of his fingers like this.

31:11.810 --> 31:14.080
你似乎对灭霸很了解
You seem to know a great deal about Thanos.

31:14.690 --> 31:18.710
卡魔拉是灭霸的女儿
Gamora is the daughter of Thanos.

31:22.440 --> 31:24.800
你父亲杀了我弟弟
Your father killed my brother.

31:24.900 --> 31:25.850
天呐
Oh, boy.

31:26.240 --> 31:28.070
严格讲是继父
Stepfather, technically.

31:28.070 --> 31:29.770
她跟你一样恨他
And she hates him as much as you do.

31:33.660 --> 31:34.980
家家有本难念的经
Families can be tough.

31:35.290 --> 31:36.620
我父亲死前
Before my father died,

31:36.620 --> 31:38.750
才跟我说我还有个异母姐姐
he told me that I had a half-sister...

31:38.750 --> 31:40.320
被他囚禁在了地狱
that he imprisoned in Hel.

31:41.090 --> 31:44.210
然后她回了家  捅瞎了我的眼睛
And then she returned home and stabbed me in the eye.

31:44.220 --> 31:45.760
于是我不得不杀了她
So I had to kill her.

31:45.760 --> 31:47.490
人生啊  是吧
That's life though, isn't it, I guess.

31:47.930 --> 31:49.450
兜兜转转
Goes round and round and...

31:50.100 --> 31:50.930
我能理解你的痛苦
I feel your pain.

31:50.930 --> 31:53.560
我也能理解你的痛苦
I feel your pain as well, because...

31:53.560 --> 31:54.520
虽然这不是比赛
I mean, it's not a competition,

31:54.520 --> 31:56.230
但我也吃过不少苦
but I've been through a lot.

31:56.230 --> 31:57.890
我父亲杀了我妈
My father killed my mother.

31:57.900 --> 31:59.800
然后我不得不杀了我爸
And then I had to kill my father.

31:59.940 --> 32:01.050
那可痛苦了
That was hard.

32:01.150 --> 32:03.510
可能比杀姐姐还痛苦
Probably even harder than having to kill a sister.

32:04.150 --> 32:07.450
而且我还两眼完好无损地回来了
Plus, I came out with both my eyes, which was...

32:07.450 --> 32:09.350
我需要一把锤子  不是勺子
I need a hammer, not a spoon.

32:10.910 --> 32:13.640
这玩意怎么开  有什么...
How do I open this thing? Is there some sort of, uh...

32:14.370 --> 32:17.360
四位密码  是生日吗
A four-digit code, maybe? Maybe a birthdate.

32:18.080 --> 32:20.400
-你干什么呢  -开走你们的飞行舱
- What are you doing? - Taking your pod.

32:21.920 --> 32:23.110
你别想
No, you're not.

32:24.960 --> 32:28.830
你今天别想开走我们的飞行舱  先生
You will not be taking our pod today, sir.

32:30.800 --> 32:33.160
奎尔  你是在故意把嗓音压低吗
Quill, are you making your voice deeper?

32:34.810 --> 32:36.170
-没有  -就有
- No. - You are.

32:36.480 --> 32:39.440
你在模仿那个男神  好奇怪
You're imitating the god-man. It's weird.

32:39.440 --> 32:40.460
我没有
No, I'm not.

32:40.560 --> 32:43.510
-他又来了  -我的嗓音就是这样
- He just did it again! - This is my voice.

32:49.070 --> 32:50.180
你在嘲笑我吗
Are you mocking me?

32:50.570 --> 32:53.230
-你在嘲笑我吗  -别闹了  你又那样了
- Are you mocking me? - Stop it. You did it again.

32:54.120 --> 32:55.410
他想模仿我
He's trying to copy me.

32:55.410 --> 32:56.250
你给我停下
I need you to stop doing that.

32:56.250 --> 32:57.910
-够了  -他先开始的
- Enough! - He's doing it first.

32:57.910 --> 32:59.580
我们得阻止灭霸
We need to stop Thanos.

32:59.580 --> 33:01.210
所以  我们得查明
Which means we need to find out

33:01.210 --> 33:02.130
他接下来要去哪
where he's going next.

33:02.130 --> 33:03.110
虚无知地 [不去哪]
Knowhere.

33:03.710 --> 33:05.460
他肯定会去什么地方的
He must be going somewhere.

33:05.460 --> 33:07.240
不对  虚无知地吗
No, no. Knowhere?

33:07.720 --> 33:09.870
那是个地方  我们去过  烂爆了
It's a place. We've been there. It sucks.

33:10.550 --> 33:12.790
-抱歉  那是我们的食物  -现在不是了
- Excuse me, that's our food. - Not anymore.

33:13.390 --> 33:16.420
托尔  他为什么要去虚无知地
Thor, why would he go to Knowhere?

33:16.720 --> 33:17.930
因为多年来
Because for years...

33:17.930 --> 33:20.270
现实宝石一直安全地放在那里
the Reality Stone's been safely stored there

33:20.270 --> 33:21.850
在一个叫收藏者的人手上
with a man called the Collector.

33:21.850 --> 33:23.860
如果是在收藏者手上  那就不安全了
If it's with the Collector, then it's not safe.

33:23.860 --> 33:25.400
只有白痴才会把宝石交给那人
Only an idiot would give that man a stone.

33:25.400 --> 33:26.980
-或是天才  -你怎么知道
- Or a genius. - How do you know...

33:26.980 --> 33:29.180
他不会去找其他的哪颗宝石
he's not going for one of the other stones?

33:29.650 --> 33:31.680
一共有六颗宝石
There are six stones out there.

33:32.320 --> 33:34.700
灭霸已经拿到了力量宝石
Thanos already has the Power Stone...

33:34.700 --> 33:38.270
那是他上周摧毁山达尔星时偷走的
because he stole it last week when he decimated Xandar.

33:38.450 --> 33:40.440
他从我这儿偷走了空间宝石
He stole the Space Stone from me...

33:40.540 --> 33:43.360
还摧毁了我的飞船  杀了我一半人民
when he destroyed my ship and slaughtered half my people.

33:43.580 --> 33:45.540
时间和心灵宝石在地球上很安全
The Time and Mind Stones are safe on Earth.

33:45.540 --> 33:46.540
在复仇者联盟手里
They're with the Avengers.

33:46.550 --> 33:48.920
-复仇者联盟  -地球最强大的英雄
- The Avengers? - Earth's mightiest heroes.

33:48.920 --> 33:50.010
就像凯文·贝肯吗
Like Kevin Bacon?

33:50.010 --> 33:51.420
或许有他吧  我不知道
He may be on the team. I don't know.

33:51.430 --> 33:52.800
我挺久没回去了
I haven't been there in a while.

33:52.800 --> 33:55.260
至于灵魂宝石  根本没人见过
As for the Soul Stone, well, no one's ever seen that.

33:55.260 --> 33:56.710
都没人知道它在哪
No one even knows where it is.

33:56.930 --> 33:58.640
因此灭霸得不到它
Therefore Thanos can't get it.

33:58.640 --> 34:00.350
因此他会去虚无知地
Therefore he's going to Knowhere.

34:00.350 --> 34:02.670
好拿到现实宝石
Hence he'll be getting the Reality Stone.

34:03.020 --> 34:03.800
不客气
You're welcome.

34:03.850 --> 34:05.520
那我们得马上去虚无知地
Then we have to go to Knowhere now.

34:05.520 --> 34:09.680
不  我们得去尼德威阿尔
Wrong. Where we have to go is Nidavellir.

34:09.740 --> 34:11.610
-那个词是编出来的  -所有词都是编出来的
- That's a made-up word. - All words are made up.

34:11.610 --> 34:14.720
尼德威阿尔是真的  你认真的吗
Nidavellir is real? Seriously?

34:14.870 --> 34:16.120
那地方是个传奇
That place is a legend.

34:16.120 --> 34:18.270
他们能造出最强大  最可怕的武器
They make the most powerful, horrific weapons

34:18.370 --> 34:20.080
来折腾整个宇宙
to ever torment the universe.

34:20.080 --> 34:22.370
我可是非常愿意去的
I would very much like to go there, please.

34:22.370 --> 34:23.330
这只兔子说的对
The rabbit is correct

34:23.330 --> 34:25.040
它显然是你们当中最聪明的
and clearly the smartest among you.

34:25.040 --> 34:27.950
-兔子  -只有矮人伊特里能造出我需要的武器
- Rabbit?  - Only Eitri the Dwarf can make me the weapon I need.

34:28.670 --> 34:29.880
你就是船长吧  先生
I assume you're the captain, sir.

34:29.880 --> 34:30.960
有眼光
You're very perceptive.

34:30.970 --> 34:32.300
你看起来像个高贵的领袖
You seem like a noble leader.

34:32.300 --> 34:34.050
你愿意跟我一起去尼德威阿尔吗
Will you join me on my quest to Nidavellir?

34:34.050 --> 34:37.050
让我问下船长  等一下  我就是船长
Let me just ask the captain. Oh, wait a second, it's me!

34:37.050 --> 34:38.710
-好  我加入  -太棒了
- Yeah. I'll go. - Wonderful!

34:39.100 --> 34:40.560
不过  我才是船长
Except for that I'm the captain.

34:40.560 --> 34:41.100
安静
Quiet.

34:41.100 --> 34:42.980
-那是我的背包  -坐下吧你
- That's my backpack. - Go sit down.

34:42.980 --> 34:44.770
这是我的飞船
Look, this is my ship.

34:44.770 --> 34:46.130
我才不会去什么...
And I'm not goin' to...

34:47.570 --> 34:49.860
等一下  那是什么样的武器
Wait, what kinda weapon are we talkin' about here?

34:49.860 --> 34:51.550
能杀灭霸的那种
The Thanos-killing kind.

34:51.940 --> 34:53.610
你不觉得我们每个人都应该弄把那样的武器吗
Don't you think that we should all have a weapon like that?

34:53.610 --> 34:55.780
不  你们没有驾驭它们的力量
No. You simply lack the strength to wield them.

34:55.780 --> 34:56.740
你们的身体会碎裂
Your bodies would crumble

34:56.740 --> 34:58.410
思维会崩溃  甚至疯掉
as your minds collapsed into madness.

34:58.410 --> 35:00.160
我现在更想要了  会不会很奇怪
Is it weird that I wanna do it even more now?

35:00.160 --> 35:01.240
没错  是有一点
Mmm, a little bit, yeah.

35:01.250 --> 35:02.830
如果我们不去虚无知地
If we don't go to Knowhere

35:02.830 --> 35:04.710
而灭霸又得到一颗宝石
and Thanos retrieves another stone...

35:04.710 --> 35:06.250
他就会强大得不可阻挡了
he'll be too powerful to stop.

35:06.250 --> 35:08.920
-他已经不可阻挡了  -我有办法了
- He already is. - I got it figured out.

35:08.920 --> 35:10.460
我们有两艘船
We got two ships

35:10.460 --> 35:12.420
和一群各种各样的白痴
and a large assortment of morons.

35:12.420 --> 35:15.050
我和格鲁特跟这位海盗天使走
So me and Groot will go with the pirate angel here.

35:15.050 --> 35:16.680
白痴们去虚无知地
And the morons will go to Knowhere

35:16.680 --> 35:18.540
试图阻止灭霸
to try to stop Thanos.

35:18.640 --> 35:20.810
-好吗  好  -很好
- Cool? Cool. - So cool.

35:20.810 --> 35:21.750
顺便说一句
For the record...

35:22.810 --> 35:23.930
我知道你跟他走
I know that you're going with him

35:23.930 --> 35:25.390
是因为灭霸不在那里
because it's where Thanos isn't.

35:25.390 --> 35:26.810
你真的不应该
You know, you really shouldn't

35:26.810 --> 35:29.590
这样跟你的船长讲话  奎尔
talk that way to your captain, Quill.

35:30.320 --> 35:31.470
走了  格鲁特
Come on, Groot.

35:32.110 --> 35:34.550
把游戏放下  你的脑子会烂掉的
Put that game down. You'll rot your brain.

35:38.570 --> 35:41.020
再会了  祝你们好运  白痴们
I bid you farewell and good luck, morons.

35:41.490 --> 35:42.230
再见
Bye.

35:57.340 --> 35:58.290
小幻
Vis?

35:58.970 --> 36:00.500
又是宝石
Is it the stone again?

36:01.060 --> 36:02.710
它好像在跟我说话
It's as if it's speaking to me.

36:03.270 --> 36:04.460
它说什么
What does it say?

36:05.940 --> 36:08.590
我...不知道  但它说了些什么
I don't... I don't know, but something.

36:21.620 --> 36:23.020
告诉我你感觉到了什么
Tell me what you feel.

36:31.090 --> 36:33.200
我只感觉到了你
I just feel you.

36:41.250 --> 36:47.170
苏  格  兰

36:41.970 --> 36:43.850
10点有一班去格拉斯哥的列车
So there's a 10:00 A.M. to Glasgow...

36:43.850 --> 36:46.060
这样你回去之前  我们还能一起多待会儿
which would give us more time together before you went back.

36:46.060 --> 36:47.460
如果我错过那班车呢
What if I miss that train?

36:47.810 --> 36:48.890
11点还有一班
There's an 11:00.

36:48.890 --> 36:50.880
如果我错过所有车次呢
What if I missed all the trains?

36:52.820 --> 36:54.650
这次我不回去了怎么样
What if this time I didn't go back?

36:54.650 --> 36:56.070
但你向斯塔克承诺过
But you gave Stark your word.

36:56.070 --> 36:57.490
我更想向你许下承诺
I'd rather give it to you.

36:57.490 --> 36:59.570
也有人在等我回去
Well, there are people who are expecting me too, you know.

36:59.570 --> 37:01.030
我们都做过承诺
We both made promises.

37:01.030 --> 37:02.100
但没有对彼此承诺
Not to each other.

37:03.530 --> 37:04.350
旺达
Wanda.

37:05.080 --> 37:07.700
两年了  我们偷来了这些相处的时光
For two years, we've stolen these moments...

37:07.710 --> 37:09.270
想看看我们是不是合得来
trying to see if this could work and...

37:09.710 --> 37:10.820
我不知道
I don't know.

37:11.580 --> 37:13.460
我只想说说自己的看法
You know what, I'm just gonna speak for myself.

37:13.460 --> 37:15.800
我觉得...
I think...

37:15.800 --> 37:16.880
-我们合得来  -是啊
- It works. - It works.

37:16.880 --> 37:17.780
是啊
It works.

37:20.630 --> 37:21.580
留下来
Stay.

37:22.800 --> 37:24.040
留下陪我
Stay with me.

37:29.350 --> 37:32.090
或者算了  如果我出格了
Or not. If I'm overstepping...

37:34.760 --> 37:38.350
<b>纽约被袭击</b>

37:39.530 --> 37:41.100
它们是什么
What are they?

37:41.610 --> 37:43.970
正是宝石警告我的东西
What the stone was warning me about.

37:44.020 --> 37:47.110
<b>托尼·斯塔克失踪</b>

37:54.000 --> 37:55.030
我得走了
I have to go.

37:55.500 --> 37:56.650
不  幻视
No, Vision.

37:57.000 --> 37:58.360
幻视  如果那是真的
Vision, if that's true,

37:59.260 --> 38:01.410
那也许回去不是最好的选择
then maybe going isn't the best idea.

38:02.220 --> 38:03.240
旺达  我...
Wanda, I...

38:03.800 --> 38:04.700
幻视
Vision!

38:33.580 --> 38:36.490
那刀刃  让我无法瞬移
The blade, it stopped me from phasing.

38:37.380 --> 38:39.820
-那可能吗  -不该这样的
- Is that even possible? - It isn't supposed to be.

38:40.340 --> 38:42.030
我的系统正在崩溃
My systems are failing.

38:42.880 --> 38:46.040
我开始觉得我们不该下床了
I'm beginning to think we should have stayed in bed.

38:48.060 --> 38:48.750
小幻
Vis!

38:58.270 --> 39:02.010
放弃宝石  她才能活
Give up the stone, and she lives.

39:39.610 --> 39:40.720
放开他
Hands off.

39:56.620 --> 39:57.980
快  快
Come on. Come on.

39:58.080 --> 39:59.780
快  你得站起来
Come on, you gotta get up.

40:00.040 --> 40:01.360
你得站起来  快
You gotta get up. Come on.

40:04.010 --> 40:04.780
我们得走了
We have to go.

40:06.800 --> 40:09.040
拜托  你走吧
Please. Please leave.

40:09.300 --> 40:10.700
你让我留下来的
You asked me to stay.

40:12.510 --> 40:13.830
-我要留下  -拜托
- I'm staying. - Please.

41:24.920 --> 41:26.700
-起来  -我起不来
- Get up. - I can't.

41:26.800 --> 41:29.120
我们不想杀你  但我们不会手软的
We don't wanna kill you, but we will.

41:29.630 --> 41:31.620
过时不候
You'll never get the chance again.

41:47.730 --> 41:48.680
你能站起来吗
Can you stand?

41:54.200 --> 41:55.560
谢谢你  队长
Thank you, Captain.

41:58.290 --> 41:59.350
先扶你上飞机吧
Let's get you on the jet.

42:03.790 --> 42:06.740
我们不是说好了吗
Now, I thought we had a deal.

42:07.460 --> 42:11.340
别走太远  保持联系  不要冒险
Stay close, check in, don't take any chances.

42:11.340 --> 42:12.240
对不起
I'm sorry.

42:12.760 --> 42:14.290
我们只是需要时间
We just wanted time.

42:17.350 --> 42:18.370
去哪里  队长
Where to, Cap?

42:21.440 --> 42:22.250
回家
Home.

42:26.150 --> 42:28.840
我们会安全的  会安全的
We'll be safe. We'll be safe.

42:53.220 --> 42:54.300
泽霍贝瑞人
Zehobereians.

42:54.300 --> 42:55.800
母亲  我母亲呢
Mother! Where's my mother?

42:55.800 --> 42:57.720
不选一边就要死
Choose a side or die.

42:57.720 --> 42:58.750
母亲
Mother!

42:59.430 --> 43:01.710
一边是启示
One side is a revelation...

43:01.980 --> 43:05.050
另一边是只有少数人拥有的荣誉
the other an honor known only to a few.

43:05.730 --> 43:07.210
你怎么了  小家伙
What's wrong, little one?

43:07.810 --> 43:11.220
我母亲  我母亲在哪
My mother. Where is my mother?

43:15.950 --> 43:17.020
你叫什么名字
What's your name?

43:18.530 --> 43:19.430
我叫卡魔拉
Gamora.

43:20.740 --> 43:22.600
你很有斗志  卡魔拉
You're quite the fighter, Gamora.

43:24.330 --> 43:25.110
来
Come.

43:25.830 --> 43:26.820
我来帮你
Let me help you.

43:40.260 --> 43:41.290
你看
Look.

43:44.980 --> 43:46.000
很漂亮是吧
Pretty, isn't it?

43:47.480 --> 43:50.880
平衡感恰到好处  正是一切事物应有的样子
Perfectly balanced, as all things should be.

43:51.110 --> 43:54.720
左右偏移太多的话...
Too much to one side or the other...

43:58.780 --> 44:01.770
给  你试试
Here. You try.

44:05.500 --> 44:09.190
安详地去见你们的造物主吧
Now, go in peace to meet your maker.

44:13.800 --> 44:15.070
集中注意力
Concentrate.

44:18.300 --> 44:21.290
这就对了  你掌握了
There. You've got it.

44:30.560 --> 44:31.340
卡魔拉
Gamora.

44:32.770 --> 44:33.610
你知不知道这些手榴弹
Do you know if these grenades

44:33.610 --> 44:36.320
是炸掉蛋蛋的  还是毒气弹
are the blow-off-your-junk kind or the gas kind?

44:36.320 --> 44:37.000
因为我想
Because I was thinking about

44:37.000 --> 44:39.180
在皮带上挂几个
hanging a couple on my belt right here.

44:39.200 --> 44:40.070
但我可不想被炸...
But I don't want to if they're the...

44:40.070 --> 44:41.520
我需要你帮忙
I need to ask a favor.

44:42.450 --> 44:43.480
当然
Yeah, sure.

44:45.290 --> 44:46.250
不管怎样
One way or another,

44:46.250 --> 44:48.730
我们都会与灭霸交手的
the path that we're on leads to Thanos.

44:50.460 --> 44:52.530
这就是手榴弹的用处
Which is what the grenades are for.

44:53.630 --> 44:55.660
抱歉  你要我帮什么忙
I'm sorry. What's the favor?

44:57.470 --> 44:58.780
如果事情出了岔子
If things go wrong...

45:00.260 --> 45:02.250
如果灭霸抓到了我
If Thanos gets me...

45:06.930 --> 45:08.670
我要你答应我
I want you to promise me...

45:09.900 --> 45:10.920
你会杀了我
you'll kill me.

45:11.860 --> 45:12.630
什么
What?

45:15.900 --> 45:18.300
我知道一些他不知道的事
I know something he doesn't.

45:20.950 --> 45:22.390
如果他知道了
And if he finds it out,

45:23.120 --> 45:25.200
那整个宇宙都有危险了
the entire universe could be at risk.

45:25.200 --> 45:26.330
你知道什么
What do you know?

45:26.330 --> 45:28.190
如果我告诉你  你也知道了
If I tell you, you'd know too.

45:31.500 --> 45:33.230
如果这事如此重要
If it's so important...

45:33.460 --> 45:34.440
难道我不该知道吗
shouldn't I?

45:34.630 --> 45:35.750
除非你想死
Only if you wanna die.

45:35.750 --> 45:37.990
为什么总有人要死
Why does somebody always have to die in this scenario?

45:39.090 --> 45:39.820
你就
Just...

45:42.430 --> 45:45.370
相信我  可能还要杀了我
Trust me. And possibly kill me.

45:45.510 --> 45:47.890
我倒是愿意
I mean, I'd like to.

45:47.890 --> 45:49.830
真的  但是你...
I really would. But you...

45:50.020 --> 45:51.210
向我发誓
Swear to me.

45:54.820 --> 45:56.510
以你母亲的名义向我发誓
Swear to me on your mother.

46:04.450 --> 46:05.180
好
Okay.

46:11.210 --> 46:11.940
好吧
Okay.

46:28.930 --> 46:29.810
老兄
Dude.

46:29.810 --> 46:31.380
你在那里站了多久
How long have you been standing there?

46:31.600 --> 46:32.460
一小时
An hour.

46:32.810 --> 46:33.840
一小时
An hour?

46:34.690 --> 46:35.840
你不是吧
Are you serious?

46:36.110 --> 46:37.880
我已经掌握了
I've mastered the ability

46:38.230 --> 46:41.180
纹丝不动站立的能力
of standing so incredibly still...

46:42.400 --> 46:44.510
肉眼是看不到我的
that I become invisible to the eye.

46:45.490 --> 46:46.310
看好了
Watch.

46:49.870 --> 46:51.940
你在吃花生糖呢
You're eating a zarg-nut.

46:52.500 --> 46:53.570
但是我的动作
But my movement...

46:54.670 --> 46:56.030
如此缓慢
was so slow...

46:57.130 --> 46:58.590
令人难以察觉
that it's imperceptible.

46:58.590 --> 47:00.240
不是
Mmm, no.

47:01.590 --> 47:02.670
我坚信没人能看到我
I'm sure I'm invisible.

47:02.670 --> 47:04.120
德拉克斯
Hi, Drax.

47:06.600 --> 47:07.450
该死的
Damn it.

47:19.800 --> 47:24.770
虚  无  知  地

47:27.490 --> 47:29.140
这地方似乎已经荒废了
This place looks deserted.

47:29.490 --> 47:32.080
第三象限有动静
I'm reading movement in the third quadrant.

47:32.080 --> 47:34.020
没错  我也看到了
Yep, I'm picking that up too.

47:35.710 --> 47:37.070
我们在这里降落吧
Let's put down right here.

47:48.800 --> 47:50.000
东西不在我这里
I don't have it.

47:52.640 --> 47:54.100
银河系的人都知道
Everyone in the galaxy knows

47:54.100 --> 47:55.940
你愿出卖亲兄弟
you'd sell your own brother...

47:55.940 --> 47:57.560
来为你可悲的收藏
if you thought it would add even the slightest trinket

47:57.560 --> 47:59.420
增添一点小装饰品
to your pathetic collection.

48:07.450 --> 48:10.180
我知道现实宝石在你手上  蒂万
I know you have the Reality Stone, Tivan.

48:10.740 --> 48:14.350
把宝石交给我  你就不必遭受折磨
Giving it to me will spare you a great deal of suffering.

48:17.540 --> 48:18.820
我和你说了
I told you.

48:19.960 --> 48:21.240
我卖掉了
I sold it.

48:23.840 --> 48:25.800
我为什么要骗你
Why would I lie?

48:25.800 --> 48:28.240
我想骗人是你的天性
I imagine it's like breathing for you.

48:29.300 --> 48:30.840
那是自杀
Like suicide.

48:30.850 --> 48:32.750
看来你明白啊
You do understand.

48:33.260 --> 48:36.130
就算是你也不会交出如此宝贵的东西
Not even you would surrender something so precious.

48:36.130 --> 48:38.160
我当时并不知道它是什么
I didn't know what it was.

48:38.160 --> 48:40.730
那你比我想的还蠢
Then you're more of a fool than I took you for.

48:41.340 --> 48:41.850
是他
It's him.

48:41.850 --> 48:43.810
最后的机会  你这骗子
Last chance, charlatan.

48:45.250 --> 48:46.820
宝石呢
Where's the stone?

48:47.510 --> 48:48.350
今天
Today...

48:49.010 --> 48:49.770
德拉克斯
Drax. Drax.

48:49.770 --> 48:52.200
他要为我妻女的死付出代价
...he pays for the deaths of my wife and daughter.

48:52.240 --> 48:53.450
德拉克斯  等等
Drax, wait.

48:54.630 --> 48:56.030
别急  别急
Not yet, not yet, not yet.

48:56.040 --> 48:57.010
德拉克斯
Drax.

49:01.250 --> 49:03.590
德拉克斯  听我说
Drax, Drax, Drax. Listen to me.

49:03.590 --> 49:05.650
他还没拿到宝石
He doesn't have the stone yet.

49:06.130 --> 49:08.420
如果我们拿到宝石  就能阻止他
If we get it, then we can stop him.

49:08.570 --> 49:11.570
我们得先拿到宝石  没错
We have to get the stone first. Yeah.

49:11.990 --> 49:12.670
不
No.

49:13.120 --> 49:16.350
不  为了奥薇特  为了卡玛莉亚
No. For Ovette, for Camaria.

49:16.760 --> 49:18.040
睡吧
Sleep.

49:30.200 --> 49:30.930
好吧
Okay.

49:31.090 --> 49:35.480
卡魔拉  螳螂  你们去右边
Gamora, Mantis, you go right.

49:36.680 --> 49:38.080
另一个右边
The other right.

50:02.150 --> 50:03.670
为什么
Why?

50:13.770 --> 50:17.290
为什么是你  女儿
Why you, daughter?

50:36.550 --> 50:37.630
好快啊
That was quick.

50:43.280 --> 50:48.220
了不起  了不起  了不起
Magnificent! Magnificent! Magnificent!

50:50.540 --> 50:53.430
你难过了吗  女儿
Is that sadness I sense in you, daughter?

50:56.380 --> 50:58.890
我心里知道  你依然在乎我
In my heart, I knew you still cared.

51:06.360 --> 51:08.600
但毕竟没法确定
But one never knows for sure.

51:18.740 --> 51:21.250
现实往往令人失望
Reality is often disappointing.

51:24.750 --> 51:26.660
至少以前是的
That is, it was.

51:28.970 --> 51:29.830
现在
Now...

51:32.500 --> 51:35.280
现实可以任我摆布了
reality can be whatever I want.

51:36.730 --> 51:38.030
你早知道我会来
You knew I'd come.

51:38.370 --> 51:39.860
我就指望着呢
I counted on it.

51:40.740 --> 51:43.120
我们需要谈谈  小家伙
There's something we need to discuss, little one.

51:48.320 --> 51:50.030
灭霸
Thanos!

51:57.760 --> 51:58.790
不
No!

52:03.150 --> 52:04.810
放了她  奶昔大哥
Let her go, Grimace.

52:05.360 --> 52:06.160
彼得
Peter.

52:07.620 --> 52:09.020
我叫你走右边的
I told you to go right.

52:09.380 --> 52:10.790
现在还说这个
Now? Really?

52:10.790 --> 52:12.180
你放了她
You let her go!

52:12.650 --> 52:14.710
你是那个男友
Ah, the boyfriend.

52:14.710 --> 52:15.510
不
No.

52:15.790 --> 52:17.120
我更喜欢自视为
Like to think of myself more as a

52:17.130 --> 52:19.860
杀泰坦的长期炮友
Titan-killing, long-term booty call.

52:19.860 --> 52:21.940
-放了她  -彼得
- Let her go. - Peter.

52:21.940 --> 52:26.760
否则我轰掉你阴囊一样的下巴
I'm gonna blow that nutsack of a chin right off your face.

52:27.180 --> 52:28.130
不是他
Not him.

52:39.210 --> 52:42.540
你答应过我  你答应了
You promised. You promised.

52:47.150 --> 52:48.310
女儿
Oh, daughter.

52:48.750 --> 52:50.710
你对他提的要求他做不到
You expect too much from him.

52:54.980 --> 52:56.710
她跟你提过了  是吧
She's asked, hasn't she?

53:00.410 --> 53:01.110
动手吧
Do it.

53:07.690 --> 53:08.660
动手
Do it!

53:16.020 --> 53:17.490
我叫你走右边的
I told you to go right.

53:19.350 --> 53:21.570
我爱你超过一切
I love you more than anything.

53:25.560 --> 53:26.670
我也爱你
I love you too.

53:41.260 --> 53:42.480
我喜欢他
I like him.

54:13.120 --> 54:14.600
幻视还没消息吗
Still no word from Vision?

54:14.950 --> 54:17.600
卫星在爱丁堡附近跟丢了他
Satellites lost him somewhere over Edinburgh.

54:17.630 --> 54:19.240
驾驶盗走的昆式战斗机
On a stolen Quinjet

54:19.240 --> 54:21.580
还有四个全球头号通缉犯
with four of the world's most wanted criminals.

54:21.580 --> 54:22.800
你知道他们是"罪犯"
You know they're only criminals

54:22.800 --> 54:24.870
只是因为你非要那么称呼他们
because you've chosen to call them that, right, sir?

54:24.870 --> 54:25.790
天呐  罗德
My God, Rhodes.

54:25.790 --> 54:29.280
你鬼扯的本事能跟我有一拼了
Your talent for horseshit rivals my own.

54:29.280 --> 54:30.660
要不是因为《协议》
If it weren't for those Accords,

54:30.660 --> 54:32.580
幻视根本不会走
Vision would've been right here.

54:32.970 --> 54:36.210
我记得你也签了那份文件  中校
I remember your signature on those papers, Colonel.

54:36.740 --> 54:37.550
是啊
That's right.

54:39.810 --> 54:41.500
我也为此付出了代价
And I'm pretty sure I paid for that.

54:41.720 --> 54:43.170
你后悔了吗
You have second thoughts?

54:43.170 --> 54:44.360
现在没了
Not anymore.

54:50.610 --> 54:51.810
国务卿先生
Mr. Secretary.

54:56.780 --> 54:58.450
你好大胆
You got some nerve.

54:58.980 --> 55:00.150
这我承认
I'll give you that.

55:00.880 --> 55:02.630
你现在正需要点胆呢
You could use some of that right now.

55:03.580 --> 55:05.380
世界有危险了
The world's on fire.

55:06.460 --> 55:09.830
你觉得一切都被原谅了吗
And you think all is forgiven?

55:10.210 --> 55:11.810
我想要的不是原谅
I'm not looking for forgiveness.

55:12.060 --> 55:13.980
我更不想征求同意了
And I'm way past asking permission.

55:16.260 --> 55:18.000
地球刚失去了最好的守卫者
Earth just lost her best defender.

55:18.790 --> 55:19.890
我们是来战斗的
So we're here to fight.

55:21.580 --> 55:23.090
如果你想挡路
And if you wanna stand in our way...

55:24.510 --> 55:25.610
我们连你一起打
we'll fight you too.

55:30.020 --> 55:31.020
逮捕他们
Arrest them.

55:31.840 --> 55:32.790
这就去
All over it.

55:38.490 --> 55:39.810
得上军事法庭了
That's a court-martial.

55:42.450 --> 55:43.650
见到你真高兴  队长
It's great to see you, Cap.

55:44.350 --> 55:45.450
你也是  罗德
You too, Rhodey.

55:50.140 --> 55:50.970
你们
You guys...

55:51.750 --> 55:53.100
看上去状况真差
really look like crap.

55:53.960 --> 55:55.490
这几年很辛苦吧
Must've been a rough couple years.

55:55.610 --> 55:58.470
是啊  没怎么住五星酒店
Yeah, well, the hotels weren't exactly five star.

55:58.790 --> 56:00.810
我觉得你们看上去很棒
I think you look great.

56:08.050 --> 56:09.290
是啊  我回来了
Yeah, I'm back.

56:11.750 --> 56:12.650
你好啊  布鲁斯
Hi, Bruce.

56:18.270 --> 56:19.030
小娜
Nat.

56:22.770 --> 56:24.000
好尴尬
This is awkward.

56:26.650 --> 56:28.560
那他们还会再回来吧
So we gotta assume they're coming back, right?

56:28.560 --> 56:29.810
他们显然能找到我们
And they can clearly find us.

56:29.810 --> 56:31.950
我们得全体出动  克林特呢
We need all hands on deck. Where's Clint?

56:32.240 --> 56:33.520
《协议》的事后
After the whole Accords situation,

56:33.520 --> 56:35.270
他和斯科特做了协议
he and Scott took a deal.

56:35.270 --> 56:37.160
他们的家人承受不了  所以他们被软禁在家了
It was too tough on their families. They're on house arrest.

56:37.160 --> 56:38.470
-斯科特是谁  -蚁人
- Who's Scott? - Ant-Man.

56:38.470 --> 56:40.390
有蚁人还有蜘蛛侠
There's an Ant-Man and a Spider-Man?

56:41.000 --> 56:42.000
好吧
Okay, look.

56:42.050 --> 56:45.120
灭霸有全宇宙最大的军队
Thanos has the biggest army in the universe...

56:45.120 --> 56:48.730
他不会罢休的  除非他得到
and he is not gonna stop until he gets...

56:50.690 --> 56:51.600
幻视的宝石
Vision's stone.

56:51.600 --> 56:52.970
那我们得保护它
Then we have to protect it.

56:53.030 --> 56:54.800
不  我们得毁掉它
No, we have to destroy it.

56:56.850 --> 56:58.310
我好好想过了
I've been giving a good deal of thought

56:58.310 --> 56:59.510
我脑袋上的这东西
to this entity in my head.

56:59.510 --> 57:01.310
关于它的性质
About its nature.

57:01.440 --> 57:03.770
以及它的组成
But also its composition.

57:03.770 --> 57:05.570
我觉得如果它遭遇
I think if it were exposed

57:05.750 --> 57:08.080
足够强大的能量源
to a sufficiently powerful energy source...

57:08.080 --> 57:11.870
特性类似其本身的能量  那或许
something very similar to its own signature, perhaps...

57:13.230 --> 57:15.670
它的分子完整性就会被破坏
its molecular integrity could fail.

57:16.120 --> 57:18.070
你也会随之被摧毁
Yeah, and you with it.

57:18.790 --> 57:20.370
这不是个选择
We're not having this conversation.

57:20.370 --> 57:22.320
只有销毁宝石
Eliminating the stone is the only way

57:22.320 --> 57:24.510
才能确保灭霸拿不到它
to be certain that Thanos can't get it.

57:25.060 --> 57:27.200
那代价太高了
That's too high a price.

57:31.730 --> 57:34.470
只有你有能力付出这代价
Only you have the power to pay it.

57:38.350 --> 57:40.490
灭霸威胁宇宙一半的生命
Thanos threatens half the universe.

57:40.510 --> 57:43.000
不能让一人的生命阻碍战胜他的希望
One life cannot stand in the way of defeating him.

57:43.230 --> 57:44.380
这样不对
But it should.

57:47.150 --> 57:48.120
我们不以命换命  幻视
We don't trade lives, Vision.

57:48.120 --> 57:50.960
队长  70年前  你付出生命
Captain, 70 years ago, you laid down your life...

57:50.960 --> 57:52.540
来挽救了多少人
to save how many millions of people?

57:52.540 --> 57:54.640
告诉我  这有什么不同
Tell me, why is this any different?

57:55.010 --> 57:57.490
因为  你可能还有选择
Because you might have a choice.

57:58.590 --> 57:59.860
你的心灵是由
Your mind is made up

57:59.870 --> 58:02.560
许多东西叠加而成的
of a complex construct of overlays.

58:02.560 --> 58:06.250
贾维斯  奥创  托尼  我  宝石
Jarvis, Ultron, Tony, me, the stone.

58:06.250 --> 58:08.090
他们混在了一起
All of them mixed together,

58:08.090 --> 58:09.980
彼此学习
all of them learning from one another.

58:09.980 --> 58:11.920
你是说幻视并不只是那块宝石
You're saying Vision isn't just the stone?

58:11.920 --> 58:14.860
我是说  如果我们取出宝石
I'm saying that if we take out the stone...

58:15.150 --> 58:16.820
还剩下不少的幻视
there's still a whole lot of Vision left.

58:16.820 --> 58:18.410
或许还是最好的部分
Perhaps the best parts.

58:18.490 --> 58:19.580
这能做到吗
Can we do that?

58:20.510 --> 58:21.810
我在这里是不行
Not me, not here.

58:22.610 --> 58:24.100
那你最好赶紧找到
Well, you better find someone

58:24.100 --> 58:25.570
合适的地方和人
and somewhere fast.

58:25.570 --> 58:26.700
罗斯可不会让你们
Ross isn't just gonna let you guys

58:26.700 --> 58:28.310
再回老房间住
have your old rooms back.

58:31.240 --> 58:32.270
我知道个地方
I know somewhere.

58:46.410 --> 58:49.330
瓦  坎  达

58:47.570 --> 58:48.390
御林护卫
The Kingsguard

58:48.390 --> 58:50.480
和女子皇家护卫队都已得到通知
and the Dora Milaje have been alerted.

58:50.480 --> 58:51.710
边境部落呢
And the Border Tribe?

58:52.190 --> 58:53.500
还剩的都通知了
Those that are left.

58:54.140 --> 58:56.170
派人传话去贾巴里
Send word to the Jabari as well.

58:56.490 --> 58:58.550
姆巴库也喜欢好好打一场
M'Baku likes a good fight.

59:00.700 --> 59:01.890
他呢
And what of this one?

59:03.060 --> 59:05.240
他可能已经厌倦了战争
This one may be tired of war.

59:05.640 --> 59:08.480
但白狼已经休息够久了
But the White Wolf has rested long enough.

59:31.340 --> 59:32.350
哪里要打仗了
Where's the fight?

59:33.820 --> 59:34.880
他们就来
On its way.

59:53.720 --> 59:56.180
我为灭霸效力这么久
In all the time I've served Thanos...

59:58.120 --> 59:59.630
从未让他失望过
I have never failed him.

01:00:05.190 --> 01:00:07.890
如果我赶到了我们泰坦星的汇合点
If I were to reach our rendezvous on Titan...

01:00:08.370 --> 01:00:09.900
而时间宝石还连在
with the Time Stone still attached

01:00:09.900 --> 01:00:12.020
你这讨厌鬼身上
to your vaguely irritating person...

01:00:12.320 --> 01:00:14.810
我会受到  责罚的
there would be judgment.

01:00:23.640 --> 01:00:24.570
给我
Give me...

01:00:29.290 --> 01:00:30.320
宝石
the stone.

01:00:42.990 --> 01:00:45.040
你还真是件忠心耿耿的外套啊
You're a seriously loyal piece of outerwear, aren't you?

01:00:45.040 --> 01:00:47.030
说到忠诚
Yeah, uh, speaking of loyalty...

01:00:48.030 --> 01:00:48.900
什么...
What the...

01:00:48.900 --> 01:00:50.590
-我知道你要说什么  -你不该在这儿的
- I know what you're gonna say. - You should not be here.

01:00:50.590 --> 01:00:51.730
-我本想回家的  -我不想听
- I was gonna go home. - I don't wanna hear it.

01:00:51.730 --> 01:00:52.770
但下去的路好远啊
But it was such a long way down

01:00:52.770 --> 01:00:53.570
我路上就在想你
and I just thought about you on the way...

01:00:53.570 --> 01:00:54.280
你还说上了
And now I gotta hear it.

01:00:54.290 --> 01:00:55.530
然后我就卡在飞船边上了
...and kinda stuck to the side of the ship.

01:00:55.530 --> 01:00:58.160
这件战衣的直觉特别准
And this suit is ridiculously intuitive,

01:00:58.160 --> 01:00:58.660
-真的  -该死
- by the way. - God damn it.

01:00:58.660 --> 01:01:01.370
所以如果要说  我在这儿其实怪你
So, if anything, it's kinda your fault that I'm here.

01:01:01.950 --> 01:01:03.450
-你说什么  -我收回
- What did you just say? - I take that back.

01:01:03.450 --> 01:01:04.830
现在  我在外太空里了
And now, I'm here in space.

01:01:04.830 --> 01:01:07.270
是啊  在我不想要你在的地方
Yeah, right where I didn't want you to be.

01:01:07.880 --> 01:01:09.810
这里不是科尼岛  不是学校出游
This isn't Coney Island. This isn't a field trip.

01:01:09.810 --> 01:01:11.090
这可是有去无回
This is a one-way ticket.

01:01:11.090 --> 01:01:13.020
听到了吗  别假装你都想清楚了
You hear me? Don't pretend you thought this through.

01:01:13.020 --> 01:01:13.810
不  我想清楚了
No, I did think this through.

01:01:13.810 --> 01:01:15.490
你根本不可能想清楚了
You could not have possibly thought this through.

01:01:15.490 --> 01:01:17.230
我想当个友好邻居蜘蛛侠
You can't be a friendly neighborhood Spider-Man...

01:01:17.230 --> 01:01:18.630
但没有邻居了还怎么做
if there's no neighborhood.

01:01:21.180 --> 01:01:21.980
好吧  这话不是很通
Okay, that didn't really make sense,

01:01:21.990 --> 01:01:23.350
但你明白我想说什么
but you know what I'm trying to say.

01:01:26.540 --> 01:01:27.890
好了  还有情况要处理呢
Come on. We got a situation.

01:01:29.630 --> 01:01:30.540
看到下面那个了吗  他有麻烦
See him down there? He's in trouble.

01:01:30.540 --> 01:01:31.470
你有什么计划
What's your plan?

01:01:31.790 --> 01:01:32.460
说吧
Go.

01:01:33.640 --> 01:01:34.600
好吧
Okay, okay...

01:01:35.330 --> 01:01:38.110
好吧  你看过一部特老的电影《异形》吗
Okay. Did you ever see this really old movie, Aliens?

01:01:42.300 --> 01:01:44.040
疼吧  是不是
Painful, aren't they?

01:01:45.130 --> 01:01:47.760
原本是用来做显微手术的
