You don't know that!

01:07:17.520 --> 01:07:20.050
只有我知道这个道理
I'm the only one who knows that.

01:07:20.330 --> 01:07:24.390
至少  只有我愿意为此采取行动
At least, I'm the only one with the will to act on it.

01:07:26.250 --> 01:07:27.250
曾经
