01:08:49.970 --> 01:08:51.270
求你别这样
Please don't do this.

01:08:51.280 --> 01:08:53.410
还差点成功了
And very nearly succeeded.

01:08:54.160 --> 01:08:55.670
所以我把她带来了这里
So I brought her here.

01:08:57.200 --> 01:08:58.390
好跟她谈谈
To talk.

01:09:05.940 --> 01:09:08.350
