01:13:58.180 --> 01:13:59.600
你该洗洗的
I would've washed that.

01:14:00.790 --> 01:14:03.690
我唯一能把它从康特西亚偷出来的办法就是塞进我
The only way I could sneak it off Contraxia was up my...

01:14:04.200 --> 01:14:05.290
我们到了
Hey, we're here!

01:14:09.900 --> 01:14:11.030
这玩意好像不好使
I don't think this thing works.

01:14:11.030 --> 01:14:12.410
怎么暗乎乎的
Everything seems dark.

01:14:14.610 --> 01:14:16.090
不是眼睛的问题
It ain't the eye.

01:14:29.770 --> 01:14:30.930
情况不对
Something's wrong.

01:14:31.980 --> 01:14:33.460
中子星熄灭了
The star's gone out.

01:14:34.660 --> 01:14:36.160
环也冻住了
And the rings are frozen.

01:14:40.070 --> 01:14:45.570
尼  德  威  阿  尔

01:14:57.070 --> 01:14:58.080
希望这些矮人
I hope these dwarves

01:14:58.080 --> 01:15:00.430
铸造的本事比打扫强
are better at forging than they are cleaning.

01:15:05.580 --> 01:15:06.470
或许他们是意识到
Maybe they realized that

01:15:06.470 --> 01:15:08.890
自己住在太空里的一个垃圾堆里
they live in a junk pile in the middle of space.

01:15:08.900 --> 01:15:11.630
这个锻炉几世纪都没熄过火了
This forge hasn't gone dark in centuries.

01:15:14.140 --> 01:15:17.000
你说灭霸有个手套  是吧
You said Thanos had a gauntlet, right?

01:15:17.000 --> 01:15:18.270
对  怎么
Yes, why?

01:15:18.420 --> 01:15:20.100
像那样的吗
It look anything like that?

01:15:23.670 --> 01:15:25.410
我是格鲁特
I am Groot.

01:15:25.620 --> 01:15:26.780
回飞行舱去
Go back to the pod.

01:15:31.470 --> 01:15:32.640
伊特里  等等
Eitri, wait!

01:15:33.260 --> 01:15:34.000
住手
Stop!

01:15:35.300 --> 01:15:36.000
住手
Stop.

01:15:37.060 --> 01:15:37.990
托尔
Thor?

01:15:41.170 --> 01:15:42.490
这里发生了什么
What happened here?

01:15:42.950 --> 01:15:45.470
你本该保护我们的
You were supposed to protect us.

01:15:46.170 --> 01:15:48.980
阿斯加德本该保护我们的
Asgard was supposed to protect us.

01:15:49.030 --> 01:15:51.370
阿斯加德被毁了
Asgard is destroyed.

01:15:53.490 --> 01:15:56.970
伊特里  手套  你做了什么
Eitri, the glove. What did you do?

01:16:09.960 --> 01:16:12.820
环上住了300个矮人
300 dwarves lived on this ring.

01:16:14.460 --> 01:16:17.430
我以为如果我听从他的命令  他们就会安全
I thought if I did what he asked, they'd be safe.

01:16:19.840 --> 01:16:21.520
我造出了他要的东西
I made what he wanted.

01:16:23.070 --> 01:16:27.390
一件能汲取宝石力量的装置
A device capable of harnessing the power of the stones.

01:16:29.540 --> 01:16:33.950
然后他还是杀了所有人
Then he killed everyone anyway.

01:16:36.610 --> 01:16:38.120
除了我
All except me.

01:16:39.460 --> 01:16:41.560
"你的命属于你"  他说
"Your life is yours," He said.

01:16:42.530 --> 01:16:46.670
"但你的手  属于我"
"But your hands are mine alone."

01:16:47.350 --> 01:16:49.660
伊特里  你的手不是重点
Eitri, this isn't about your hands.

01:16:50.620 --> 01:16:52.300
你设计的每一件武器
Every weapon you've ever designed,

01:16:52.300 --> 01:16:53.860
每把斧子  锤子  剑
every axe, hammer, sword...

01:16:53.870 --> 01:16:56.030
都在你脑袋里
it's all inside your head.

01:16:56.990 --> 01:16:58.960
我知道你现在觉得希望尽失
Now, I know it feels like all hope is lost.

01:16:58.960 --> 01:17:00.130
相信我  我知道
Trust me, I know.

01:17:00.940 --> 01:17:05.720
但你我联手  我们能杀了灭霸
But together, you and I, we can kill Thanos.

01:17:46.170 --> 01:17:48.500
螳螂  听好了
Mantis, listen very carefully.

01:17:48.840 --> 01:17:50.710
我需要你去泰坦星见我
I need you to meet me on Titan.

01:17:57.730 --> 01:17:58.380
怎么了
Hey, what's going on?

01:17:58.390 --> 01:18:00.280
我们好像到了
I think we're here.

01:18:00.280 --> 01:18:02.550
这玩意恐怕没有自动停车功能
I don't think this rig has a self-park function.

01:18:04.220 --> 01:18:06.180
把手伸到方向装置里
Get your hand inside the steering gimbal.

01:18:06.180 --> 01:18:07.350
把这个合上
Close those around it.

01:18:08.520 --> 01:18:09.470
-懂吗  -好的
- You understand? - Yep, got it.

01:18:09.470 --> 01:18:10.850
这是给一个大块头准备的
This was meant for one big guy,

01:18:10.850 --> 01:18:13.330
-我们动作得同步  -好的  好了
- so we gotta move at the same time. - Okay, okay. Ready.

01:18:17.560 --> 01:18:18.740
我们最好转向
We might wanna turn.

01:18:18.750 --> 01:18:20.410
转向  转向啊
Turn! Turn! Turn!

01:18:43.850 --> 01:18:47.770
泰  坦  星

01:18:49.850 --> 01:18:50.540
你没事吧
You all right?

01:18:52.990 --> 01:18:54.000
好悬啊
That was close.

01:18:55.700 --> 01:18:56.490
我欠你的
I owe you one.

01:18:57.380 --> 01:18:59.150
我想说  如果外星人
Let me just say, if aliens

01:18:59.360 --> 01:19:01.530
在我胸腔里植入了卵什么的
wind up implanting eggs in my chest or something...

01:19:01.530 --> 01:19:02.550
而我吃掉了你们谁  那我很抱歉
and I eat one of you, I'm sorry.

01:19:02.550 --> 01:19:05.210
余下的时间里不许你
I do not want another single pop culture reference

01:19:05.210 --> 01:19:06.570
再提流行文化梗了  懂吗
out of you for the rest of the trip. You understand?

01:19:06.570 --> 01:19:08.450
我是想说  有东西过来了
I'm trying to say that something is coming.

01:19:15.530 --> 01:19:17.120
灭霸
Thanos!

01:19:38.040 --> 01:19:39.520
拜托别把你的卵放进我身体里
Please don't put your eggs in me!

01:19:41.590 --> 01:19:42.920
别动  小丑
Stay down, clown.

01:19:48.740 --> 01:19:51.230
死吧  死亡毯子
Die, blanket of death!

01:19:56.800 --> 01:20:00.050
都别动  都给我冷静
Everybody stay where you are. Chill the eff out.

01:20:00.910 --> 01:20:02.730
我就问你一次
I'm gonna ask you this one time.

01:20:03.660 --> 01:20:04.780
卡魔拉呢
Where is Gamora?

01:20:04.780 --> 01:20:07.600
我问你个更好的  卡魔拉是谁
Yeah. I'll do you one better. Who's Gamora?

01:20:07.910 --> 01:20:10.670
我问你个更好的  为什么卡魔拉
I'll do you one better. Why is Gamora?

01:20:10.670 --> 01:20:12.600
告诉我她在哪  否则我发誓
Tell me where the girl is or I swear to you

01:20:12.600 --> 01:20:13.950
我会把这小怪物烧焦的
I'm gonna French fry this little freak.

01:20:13.950 --> 01:20:17.090
来吧  你打我的人  我打你的人  来吧
Let's do it. You shoot my guy and I'll blast him. Let's go!

01:20:17.670 --> 01:20:20.270
动手吧  奎尔  我承受得住
Do it, Quill! I can take it.

01:20:20.270 --> 01:20:21.340
不  他承受不住
No, he can't take it!

01:20:21.340 --> 01:20:22.270
她说得对  你承受不住
She's right. You can't.

01:20:22.270 --> 01:20:24.630
是吗  你不告诉我她在哪吗  好啊
Oh, yeah? You don't wanna tell me where she is? That's fine.

01:20:24.630 --> 01:20:25.820
我杀了你们三个
I'll kill all three of you

01:20:25.820 --> 01:20:27.990
然后揍到灭霸开口
and I'll beat it out of Thanos myself.

01:20:27.990 --> 01:20:28.900
从你开始
Starting with you.

01:20:28.900 --> 01:20:30.010
等等  灭霸
Wait, what, Thanos?

01:20:30.010 --> 01:20:32.350
好吧  我问你个问题
All right, let me ask you this one time.

01:20:32.790 --> 01:20:34.680
你效忠哪位主人
What master do you serve?

01:20:34.680 --> 01:20:35.750
我效忠哪位主人
What master do I serve?

01:20:35.750 --> 01:20:37.680
怎么  我该说"耶稣"吗
What am I supposed to say, "Jesus"?

01:20:38.720 --> 01:20:39.450
你是地球人
You're from Earth.

01:20:39.450 --> 01:20:40.390
我不是地球人  我是密苏里人
I'm not from Earth, I'm from Missouri.

01:20:40.390 --> 01:20:41.900
那就是地球  白痴
Yeah, that's on Earth, dipshit.

01:20:41.900 --> 01:20:42.850
你打我们干什么
What are you hassling us for?

01:20:42.860 --> 01:20:44.760
你们不是灭霸的人
So you're not with Thanos?

01:20:45.490 --> 01:20:47.280
灭霸的人
With Thanos?

01:20:48.000 --> 01:20:50.480
不  我是来杀灭霸的
No, I'm here to kill Thanos.

01:20:50.640 --> 01:20:52.550
他带走了我女人  等等  你们是谁
He took my girl. Wait, who are you?

01:20:53.390 --> 01:20:54.870
我们是复仇者  哥们
We're the Avengers, man.

01:20:54.870 --> 01:20:57.470
你们是托尔说的人
You're the ones Thor told us about.

01:20:57.610 --> 01:20:58.670
你们认识托尔
You know Thor?

01:20:58.920 --> 01:20:59.620
是啊
Yeah.

01:20:59.860 --> 01:21:02.840
高个  长得不咋样  还需要别人救
Tall guy, not that good-looking, needed saving.

01:21:02.840 --> 01:21:03.880
他现在在哪
Where is he now?

01:21:19.410 --> 01:21:21.300
这就是你的计划  用砖头拍他
This is the plan? We're gonna hit him with a brick?

01:21:21.300 --> 01:21:22.580
这是模具
It's a mold.

01:21:23.680 --> 01:21:24.880
国王的武器
A king's weapon.

01:21:25.430 --> 01:21:27.590
本该是阿斯加德最强大的
Meant to be the greatest in Asgard.

01:21:28.430 --> 01:21:31.370
理论上  它甚至能召唤彩虹桥
In theory, it could even summon the Bifrost.

01:21:31.490 --> 01:21:32.560
它有名字吗
Did it have a name?

01:21:34.190 --> 01:21:35.380
风暴斧
Stormbreaker.

01:21:35.860 --> 01:21:37.070
有点过了
That's a bit much.

01:21:38.940 --> 01:21:40.150
要怎么打造它
So how do we make it?

01:21:41.900 --> 01:21:43.830
你得重启锻炉
You'll have to restart the forge.

01:21:45.110 --> 01:21:47.330
唤醒濒死星球的核心
Awaken the heart of a dying star.

01:21:49.870 --> 01:21:52.400
兔子  启动飞行舱
Rabbit, fire up the pod.

01:21:56.160 --> 01:21:58.010
这星球遭遇了什么
The hell happened to this planet?

01:21:58.270 --> 01:22:00.030
偏离自转轴八度
It's eight degrees off its axis.

01:22:00.030 --> 01:22:02.570
引力到处都是
Gravitational pull is all over the place.

01:22:03.650 --> 01:22:06.440
我们有一个优势  他会自己来
Yeah, we got one advantage. He's coming to us.

01:22:07.530 --> 01:22:08.460
我们要利用这一点
We'll use it.

01:22:08.910 --> 01:22:10.270
好了  我有个计划
All right, I have a plan.

01:22:10.360 --> 01:22:11.660
至少有个大致轮廓
Or at least the beginnings of one.

01:22:11.660 --> 01:22:12.970
非常简单  我们引他过来
It's pretty simple. We draw him in,

01:22:12.970 --> 01:22:14.410
把他打趴下  拿到需要的东西
pin him down, get what we need.

01:22:14.530 --> 01:22:15.820
我可不想陪他跳舞[跟他纠缠]
Definitely don't wanna dance with this guy.

01:22:15.820 --> 01:22:17.520
我们只想拿手套
We just want the gauntlet.

01:22:17.890 --> 01:22:19.170
你打哈欠
Are you yawning?

01:22:20.360 --> 01:22:22.260
我讲解计划的时候你竟然打哈欠
In the middle of this, while I'm breaking it down?

01:22:22.530 --> 01:22:23.890
你听见我说的了吗
Did you hear what I said?

01:22:24.370 --> 01:22:26.730
你说"我们需要计划"之后我就没在听了
I stopped listening after you said, "We need a plan."

01:22:26.730 --> 01:22:28.240
好吧  他沉浸在自己的世界里
Okay, Mr. Clean is on his own page.

01:22:28.240 --> 01:22:30.700
他们习惯了随机应变
See, "Not winging it" isn't really what they do.

01:22:30.700 --> 01:22:32.790
那他们习惯怎么做
Uh, what exactly is it that they do?

01:22:32.790 --> 01:22:34.480
打仇恨  拉群架
Kick names, take ass.

01:22:34.480 --> 01:22:35.580
没错
Yeah, that's right.

01:22:42.560 --> 01:22:44.100
好了  请各位都过来
All right, just get over here, please.

01:22:44.310 --> 01:22:46.290
爵先生  能不能让你的伙伴们围过来
Mr. Lord, can you get your folks to circle up?

01:22:46.290 --> 01:22:48.380
别爵先生  叫我星爵就好
"Mr. Lord." Star-Lord is fine.

01:22:51.280 --> 01:22:52.470
我们得联合起来
We gotta coalesce.

01:22:52.470 --> 01:22:54.430
因为如果我们只凭一腔勇气去面对他
'Cause if all we come at him with is a plucky attitude...

01:22:54.430 --> 01:22:56.940
哥们  别说什么一腔勇气
Dude, don't call us plucky.

01:22:57.030 --> 01:22:58.430
我们不知道那是什么意思
We don't know what it means.

01:22:58.540 --> 01:23:01.180
我们很乐观  我喜欢你的计划
All right, we're optimistic, yes. I like your plan.

01:23:01.180 --> 01:23:03.840
只不过它烂透了  让我来做计划
Except it sucks, so let me do the plan...

01:23:03.850 --> 01:23:05.850
这样就完美无缺了
and that way it might be really good.

01:23:05.850 --> 01:23:07.990
告诉他你斗舞拯救宇宙的事
Tell him about the dance-off to save the universe.

01:23:07.990 --> 01:23:10.110
-什么斗舞  -不值一提
- What dance-off? - It's nothing.

01:23:10.110 --> 01:23:11.370
就像那部电影《浑身是劲》一样
Like in Footloose, the movie?

01:23:11.370 --> 01:23:12.800
就是《浑身是劲》那样
Exactly like Footloose.

01:23:13.540 --> 01:23:15.240
它依然是史上最棒的电影吗
Is it still the greatest movie in history?

01:23:15.240 --> 01:23:16.300
从来都不是
It never was.

01:23:16.480 --> 01:23:17.570
别打岔  好不好
Don't encourage this, all right?

01:23:17.570 --> 01:23:18.720
-好  -这位飞侠哥顿
- Okay. - We're getting no help

01:23:18.720 --> 01:23:20.420
-帮不上我们什么  -《飞侠哥顿》
- from Flash Gordon here. - Flash Gordon?

01:23:20.420 --> 01:23:22.400
那可是在夸我哦
By the way, that's a compliment.

01:23:22.420 --> 01:23:23.980
别忘了  我有一半人类血统
Don't forget, I'm half human.

01:23:23.980 --> 01:23:25.930
也就是说我有一半的蠢
So that 50% of me that's stupid...

01:23:26.770 --> 01:23:27.940
而你是百分百的蠢
that's 100% you.

01:23:27.940 --> 01:23:29.460
我真佩服你数学这么好
Your math is blowing my mind.

01:23:29.460 --> 01:23:30.500
打扰一下
Excuse me.

01:23:31.560 --> 01:23:35.130
你的朋友经常那样吗
But does your friend often do that?

01:23:36.390 --> 01:23:38.480
斯特兰奇  没事吧
Strange, we all right?

01:23:49.030 --> 01:23:50.070
你恢复了  你没事
You're back. You're all right.

01:23:51.150 --> 01:23:52.210
你刚刚怎么了
Hey, what was that?

01:23:52.390 --> 01:23:56.440
我推进了时间  浏览未来的可能性
I went forward in time to view alternate futures.

01:23:56.990 --> 01:23:59.780
去看即将到来的这一战所有可能出现的结果
To see all the possible outcomes of the coming conflict.

01:24:01.210 --> 01:24:02.430
你看到了多少种
How many did you see?

01:24:02.740 --> 01:24:05.190
一千四百万六百零五种
14,000,605.

01:24:06.630 --> 01:24:07.670
我们赢了几种
How many did we win?

01:24:12.840 --> 01:24:13.550
一种
One.

01:24:26.490 --> 01:24:30.700
沃  密  尔  星  球

01:24:35.930 --> 01:24:37.940
灵魂宝石最好在山上
The stone had better be up there.

01:24:40.800 --> 01:24:42.370
不然你妹妹就完了
For your sister's sake.

01:25:03.410 --> 01:25:08.410
欢迎  灭霸  阿拉尔斯之子
Welcome, Thanos, son of Alars.

01:25:10.540 --> 01:25:13.870
卡魔拉  灭霸之女
Gamora, daughter of Thanos.

01:25:14.000 --> 01:25:15.030
你认识我们
You know us?

01:25:15.130 --> 01:25:19.380
我被诅咒认识所有来到此地的人
It is my curse to know all who journey here.

01:25:20.320 --> 01:25:21.990
灵魂宝石在哪
Where is the Soul Stone?

01:25:22.720 --> 01:25:23.910
你应该知道
You should know...

01:25:25.040 --> 01:25:27.800
得到它的代价极大
it extracts a terrible price.

01:25:29.550 --> 01:25:30.870
我准备好了
I am prepared.

01:25:33.490 --> 01:25:35.710
我们一开始都这么以为
We all think that at first.

01:25:40.540 --> 01:25:42.370
但我们都错了
We are all wrong.

01:25:54.390 --> 01:25:56.480
你怎么如此熟悉这里
How is it you know this place so well?

01:25:56.840 --> 01:26:01.080
上一世我也想找无限宝石
A lifetime ago, I, too, sought the stones.

01:26:01.580 --> 01:26:04.040
甚至曾把一个攥在手里过
I even held one in my hand.

01:26:04.510 --> 01:26:08.310
但它把我流放到这里
But it cast me out, banished me here.

01:26:08.930 --> 01:26:12.780
指引别人寻找我无法拥有的珍宝
Guiding others to a treasure I cannot possess.

01:26:21.460 --> 01:26:24.490
你所寻找的就在你面前
What you seek lies in front of you.

01:26:25.320 --> 01:26:27.010
你所害怕的也在那里
As does what you fear.

01:26:28.410 --> 01:26:29.340
这是什么
What's this?

01:26:30.170 --> 01:26:31.000
代价
The price.

01:26:32.050 --> 01:26:36.460
无限宝石中  灵魂宝石很特别
Soul holds a special place among the Infinity Stones.

01:26:37.630 --> 01:26:41.610
可以说它有一定的智慧
You might say it has a certain wisdom.

01:26:43.080 --> 01:26:44.940
告诉我它需要什么
Tell me what it needs.

01:26:45.120 --> 01:26:48.520
为了确保拥有它的人
To ensure that whoever possesses it...

01:26:48.650 --> 01:26:50.610
理解它的力量
understands its power...

01:26:52.300 --> 01:26:55.830
灵魂宝石需要献祭
the stone demands a sacrifice.

01:26:56.350 --> 01:26:57.120
献祭什么
Of what?

